scripts.deploy: aws --profile personal --region us-east-1 s3 cp --cache-control 'public, max-age=86400, s-maxage=86400' --recursive ./out/ s3://findmeavaccine-web/ && npm run deploy:raw
scripts.deploy:raw: node copyToRaw && aws --profile personal --region us-east-1 s3 cp --recursive --content-type 'text/html' --cache-control 'public, max-age=300, s-maxage=300' ./out/raw/ s3://findmeavaccine-web/
scripts.kick: npm run build && npm run export && npm run deploy
